text: Karyshevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Zildyarovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 46 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 12 km from Zildyarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Karyshevo
